All Implemented Interfaces:
ExpressionVisitor
public class DefaultGrammarValidator
extends AbstractGrammarValidator

This validator is responsible to validate a JPQL query grammatically purely based on the JPA specification document.

Version:
2.5
See Also:
JSR 220: Enterprise JavaBeans™ 3.0, JSR 317: Java™ Persistence 2.0, JSR 338: Java™ Persistence 2.1,

Provisional API: This interface is part of an interim API that is still under development and expected to change significantly before reaching stability. It is available at this early stage to solicit feedback from pioneering adopters on the understanding that any code that uses this API will almost certainly be broken (repeatedly) as the API evolves.

Author:
Pascal Filion
Since:
2.4
